<P>When thou envie&s;t the man who po&s;&s;e&s;&s;eth honours; when <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> titles and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> greatne&s;s rai&s;e thy indignation, &s;eek to know <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> they came unto him; enquire by what means he was po&s;&s;e&s;&s;ed of them, and thine enmity will be turned into pity.</P>
