<P>As thou can&s;t not envy what thou would&s;t not accept, di&s;dain this cau&s;e of hatred; and drive from thy &s;oul this occa&s;ion of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> parent of cruelty.</P>
<P>If thou po&s;&s;e&s;&s;e&s;t honour, can&s;t thou envy that which is obtained
