<P>NOBILITY re&s;ideth not but in the &s;oul: nor i<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter"> there true ho|nour except in virtue.</P>
<P>The favour of princes may be <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters">ught by rank and vices: titles may be purcha&s;ed for money: but the&s;e are not <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> honour.</P>
