<P>1571 Printing in Iri&s;h characters fir&s;t in&s;tituted.</P>
<P><PB N="234" REF="027039_0236_0FD2FBCD6ECF1BC8">
1572 The great ma&s;&s;acre of prote&s;tants at Paris.</P>
<P>1573 Marby-hill in Hereford removed of it&s;elf.</P>
<P>1578 Apricots and artichokes introduced into England.</P>
