<P>Engli&s;h Ea&s;t India Company incorporated&mdash;e&s;tabli&s;hed 1600.</P>
<P>Engli&s;h Turkey Company incorporated.</P>
<P>1580 Sir Francis Drake returns from his voyage round the world, being the fir&s;t Engli&s;h circumnavigator.</P>
<P>1581 J. U&s;her, Archbi&s;hop of Armagh, born in Dublin, drew up 104 articles of religion for Ireland, 1615; which were e&s;tabli&s;hed, 1635,&mdash;Died, 1656.</P>
<P>1582 Pope Gregory introduces the new &s;tyle in Italy; the 5th. October being counted 15.</P>
