<P>The cu&s;tom of powdering the hair took its ri&s;e from &s;ome
<PB N="235" REF="027039_0237_0FD2FBCEAE60B610">
ballad &s;ingers at St. German's fair, who powdered them|&s;elves to look the more ridiculous.</P>
<P>1614 New York and New Jer&s;ey &s;ettled by the Dutch.</P>
