<P>20. Great part of the city of New York burnt.</P>
<P>30. Battle of White Plains.</P>
<P>Dec. 6. Newport, R. I taken <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">y the Briti&s;h.</P>
