<P>1779 St. Vincent taken by the French.</P>
<P>May. Suffolk, Virginia, de&s;troyed by the Briti&s;h.</P>
<P>Grenada taken by the French, July 3.</P>
<P><PB N="243" REF="027039_0245_0FD2FBDC2A766450">
